==Trivia==
*In the comics, Ajak was an archaeologist and a [[Siberia]]n-born member of the sub-race of [[Eternals]] known as the Polar Eternals.
**However, during the wide rebirth of all the [[Eternals]] (following their descend into madness and mass suicidal event), Ajak was reborn as a female. According to [[Ikaris]], Eternals commonly take advantage of the rebirth process to change appearance (and potentially gender).

==Behind the Scenes==
*Before [[Salma Hayek]] was cast as Ajak, {{WPS|Ana de Armas}}, {{WPS|Eiza González}} and {{WPS|Gina Rodriguez}} were considered for the role.
*[[Vaia Zaganas]] and [[Talila Craig]] were stunt doubles for [[Salma Hayek]] in the role of Ajak.
*[[Valentina Latyna Plascencia]] was a stand-in for [[Salma Hayek]] in the role of Ajak.

